{"tid":2026917,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邊個驚？人大今晚公布「港版國安法」　堵國安漏洞　有別23條","createTime":"2020-05-21T08:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:24:50.000Z","uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbaacddeaef5245a613a1f556e68979af1adf94","tid":2026917,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4529256/org/ea2de6d16637c5eb43b7b9e009b1c0c7.jpg/houG49kCZZIktyKOrYq9kPGvka-K6wxVrl2nxq5dp8Y?v=w800r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4529256%2Forg%2Fea2de6d16637c5eb43b7b9e009b1c0c7.jpg%2FhouG49kCZZIktyKOrYq9kPGvka-K6wxVrl2nxq5dp8Y%3Fv%3Dw800r16_9&h=ac6ce5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《香港01》獲得消息，今晚人大發言人將於記者會上公布關乎香港的重大消息。因應香港或成為國家安全隱患，今年人大會議的議程包括一項全新的「港版國安法」，堵塞香港的國安漏洞，放在《基本法》附件三在港實施，變相為香港國家安全問題部分立法。消息強調，這並非《基本法》23條立法。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，港澳辦主任夏寶龍今晚會晤全體港區政協委員，就是通報有關內容。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》23條列明：香港特別行政區應自行立法禁止任何叛國、分裂國家、煽動叛亂、顛覆中央人民政府及竊取國家機密的行為，禁止外國的政治性組織或團體在香港特別行政區進行政治活動，禁止香港特別行政區的政治性組織或團體與外國的政治性組織或團體建立聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，「港版國安法」與23條沒有關係，是獨立一條新法，堵塞香港國安漏洞，列明具體刑罰，由全國人大提案並通過後，透過放入附件三在港實施，毋須經過香港立法會立法過程。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第十八條列明，全國性法律除列於本法附件三者外，不在香港特別行政區實施。凡列於本法附件三之法律，由香港特別行政區在當地公佈或立法實施。<br />\n條文又指，全國人民代表大會常務委員會在徵詢其所屬的香港特別行政區基本法委員會和香港特別行政區政府的意見後，可對列於本法附件三的法律作出增減，任何列入附件三的法律，限於有關國防、外交和其他按本法規定不屬於香港特別行政區自治範圍的法律。"},{"pid":"812ed45fabd706747582a1203449c0f15f8b43c8","tid":2026917,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:52:11.000Z","msg":"[member]<span style=\"font-size: large;\">收皮啦連登臭串乞衣樓豬&mdash;EDO脆餅#23833</span><br />\n<br />\n(被追擊後第&ldquo;8&rdquo;個新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <span style=\"color: red;\">振朗狙擊手</span>）<br />\n<br />\n想買不死鳥風褸，點買先最抵？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔經典語錄:<br />\n&rdquo;<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">我：你食撚左飯未<br />\n你： 我食左屎啦 </span></em>&ldquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭串想反追擊但話左自己係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n(第&ldquo;6&rdquo;個新名 儲錢要供824)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q5KSy5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5KSy5P.jpg&h=6e9db0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n垃圾乞衣仔你上水未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大是大非緊仲重覆開post？屌你老母死全家</span>"},{"pid":"80d89f56a3872e2b0df87356d5cd98792d9849fe","tid":2026917,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"我好撚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54feab44432254ba57b693bf48d2157d62e33e24","tid":2026917,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"大家都感受到俾中共強姦的感覺。"},{"pid":"3787f5e5da59037f74cccbf3f7d70a7bd5db8ca0","tid":2026917,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"23條 23條"},{"pid":"ef73c87250cb4613afcf839d13fbcd18c99fb3d1","tid":2026917,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反正個龍門係佢哋度"},{"pid":"2b1c4864a1204df5ea6fbf1e8f03bca8739af1b8","tid":2026917,"uid":281899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"基本法=把L衣紙"},{"pid":"a54a55ec3c842da3e60190ff057edd0f32d8fb4e","tid":2026917,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"